    <item>
      <title>内塔尼亚胡派助手前往莫斯科寻求解决加沙人质问题</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/netanyahu-sent-aide-to-moscow-seeking-progress-on-gaza-hostages</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列总理本雅明内塔尼亚胡的办公室表示，以色列寻求俄罗斯的帮助，以推动达成释放加沙人质的协议，而美国、卡塔尔和埃及牵头的与哈马斯停火的努力进展缓慢。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/netanyahu-sent-aide-to-moscow-seeking-progress-on-gaza-hostages</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:59:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>集装箱运输公司利润因货运量创纪录和运价上涨而飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/container-carrier-profits-soar-on-record-volumes-higher-rates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新分析显示，由于红海改道后货运量创纪录且运费上涨，全球集装箱航运业第二季度利润飙升至 100 亿美元以上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/container-carrier-profits-soar-on-record-volumes-higher-rates</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 11:07:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克提议在 2025 年选举年遏制预算赤字</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/czechs-propose-another-budget-deficit-cut-for-election-year-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[捷克财政部提出了一项在 2025 年选举年削减预算赤字的计划，此举引发了执政联盟关于支出优先事项的争论，因为执政党正努力应对日益增长的公众不满情绪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-01/czechs-propose-another-budget-deficit-cut-for-election-year-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 01 Sep 2024 00:13:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
